@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow border-0">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

            <p>Last updated: <strong>December 30, 2024</strong></p>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                Futbol Report ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you use our application.
            </p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Information you provide such as your name, email address, and preferences.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Data about how you interact with the app, including clicks, views, and navigation.</li>
                <li><strong>Device Data:</strong> Information about the device you use, such as operating system and device ID.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide and maintain the app functionality.</li>
                <li>Personalize user experiences.</li>
                <li>Analyze app performance and improve our services.</li>
                <li>Communicate updates and promotional offers.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p>
                We do not sell your personal information. However, we may share your data with trusted third-party service providers to enhance your experience. All such sharing complies with applicable privacy laws.
            </p>

            <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                We implement robust security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We encourage you to use strong passwords and secure networks.
            </p>

            <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access and update your personal information.</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data.</li>
                <li>Restrict certain processing activities.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@futbolreport.com</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Football Lane, Goal City, FC 45678</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
